---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials & Reviews for Fitness Studios — SocialProof" description="Fill more classes. Keep more members. Collect real member testimonials and display them on your fitness studio's website — free for one widget." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/fitness-studios">
<style>

    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .own-your-reviews { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .own-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .own-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .own-inner p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #111; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .btn-nav { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff !important; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    footer a { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
    .steps-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .testimonials-section { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .testimonials-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .testimonials-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .testimonial-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
    .testimonial-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    .testimonial-card .stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .testimonial-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 16px; font-style: italic; }
    .testimonial-card .author { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888; font-weight: 600; font-style: normal; }
    .types-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .types-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .types-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
    .type-card { border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; }
    .type-card .emoji { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .type-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .type-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .stat-bar { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 48px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .stat-bar p { font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
    .stat-bar strong { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  
</style>
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Fill your fitness classes with<br>member testimonials that convert</h1>
    <p>Collect real reviews from your members and show them on your website — so every curious prospect sees exactly what makes your studio different.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
      <a href="/blog/testimonials-for-fitness-studios" class="btn-secondary">Read the fitness studio guide</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stat-bar">
    <strong>People trust people, not ads.</strong>
    <p>A prospect checking out your studio will scroll past every promotional claim — then stop when they see a real member saying "this place changed my life." That's the only marketing that actually converts.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <h2>Why fitness studios need on-site testimonials</h2>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📉 Trial class dropout is real</h3>
        <p>Many people try a class but never convert to members. Showing transformation stories and community testimonials on your membership page gives hesitant prospects the final nudge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🏆 Your community is your USP</h3>
        <p>The instructor quality and member vibe are what make you different from the gym down the street — but you can't describe that in an ad. Testimonials show it in members' own words.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📲 Google won't rank you on vibes</h3>
        <p>A website with real testimonials signals trust to Google and to visitors. Pages with social proof see higher time-on-site and lower bounce rates — both ranking factors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>💬 Members want to share — just make it easy</h3>
        <p>After a great class or a fitness milestone, members feel great. Send them a link in the moment. You'll be amazed how many respond when there's no friction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonials-section">
    <div class="testimonials-inner">
      <h2>What fitness studio testimonials look like</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"I've tried three other gyms in this neighborhood and nothing clicked. Six months here and I'm in the best shape of my life. The coaches actually remember your name."</p>
          <span class="author">— Marcus T., member since 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"I was intimidated to start. But from day one, the community was so welcoming. I've lost 18 pounds and made actual friends. Never expected that from a gym."</p>
          <span class="author">— Alicia R., member since 2023</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"The morning Pilates classes have become a non-negotiable part of my week. The instructor adapts to every level — I've brought four friends who all signed up."</p>
          <span class="author">— Donna K., Pilates member</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="steps-section">
    <h2>Start collecting in 10 minutes</h2>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Create your free account</h3>
        <p>Sign up at SocialProof — no credit card. You get a unique collection link immediately. No widget setup required to start collecting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Send your link at the right moment</h3>
        <p>After a great class, after a milestone, at month 3 when members are fully hooked. Text, email, WhatsApp — wherever you already communicate with members.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Display testimonials on your site</h3>
        <p>One line of code. Paste it on your membership page, your class schedule page, or your homepage. Testimonials show up automatically as they arrive.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="types-section">
    <h2>Best places to show testimonials in your studio</h2>
    <div class="types-grid">
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="emoji">💪</div>
        <h3>Membership / Pricing page</h3>
        <p>The highest-value placement. Prospects reading your pricing are already interested — testimonials here convert hesitation into sign-ups.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="emoji">📅</div>
        <h3>Class schedule page</h3>
        <p>Show instructor-specific testimonials next to each class type. Helps prospects pick their first class with confidence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="emoji">🏠</div>
        <h3>Homepage</h3>
        <p>A rotating testimonial block below your hero text reassures first-time visitors before they even scroll to pricing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="emoji">📧</div>
        <h3>Trial class confirmation email</h3>
        <p>Include 2–3 testimonials in the email you send after someone books a trial. Reduces no-shows and pre-sells the experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="own-your-reviews">
    <div class="own-inner">
      <h2>Free forever for one widget</h2>
      <p>Start free — collect unlimited testimonials from your members, embed one widget on your most important page. No credit card, no time limit.</p>
      <p>Ready to display testimonials in multiple spots (pricing page + class schedule + homepage)? Pro is $9/month — cancel any time.</p>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 8px;">Get started free</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-section">
    <blockquote>"We put testimonials on our trial class page and on the membership pricing page. The difference was immediate — people showed up to trials having already read what members said. Conversion from trial to membership went up."</blockquote>
    <cite>— Boutique fitness studio owner using SocialProof</cite>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Your members love your studio. Let your website prove it.</h2>
    <p>Start collecting testimonials today — free, no credit card, live on your site in under an hour.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Start free →</a>
  </section>
</Base>
